{"tid":565243,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩餐廳可以好似提供鋼琴比客人彈？","createTime":"2018-02-18T18:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T10:10:54.000Z","uid":12980,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"65fb036466f74bb819181ac3c0e5cd77a2f4f9e0","tid":565243,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:34:02.000Z","msg":"利申我幫朋友問既<br />\n<br />\n即係好似外國咁 某啲餐廳會有部琴比客人彈<br />\n<br />\n係咁既 女朋友就黎生日 想比個驚喜佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想搵間餐廳 可以彈 想彈首屬於兩個之間既歌送比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBudget 冇所謂 幾錢都得<br />\n最想氹到佢開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我剩係知外國有 但又唔可以叫佢過黎<br />\n因為我同佢都返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我會突然返hk 一個禮拜 比個surprise 佢<br />\n<br />\n咁多位巴打比啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56806d96ff21f5910a5d3d732778ac5ee23cdea","tid":565243,"uid":6878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T19:03:58.000Z","msg":"張敬軒新開個間旋轉餐廳可能得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b800ef1fa3e8c957c0c96f448d4c60262c6075","tid":565243,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T01:17:45.000Z","msg":"樓主終於有女？"},{"pid":"1d9b585bc5c72ca8acaacc922b2d957a04394576","tid":565243,"uid":33875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T02:24:24.000Z","msg":"我屋企有座琴，又有牛扒"},{"pid":"1a66c3d562c369632f0a5bccbaa0bbc1e1ae8684","tid":565243,"uid":153418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T02:45:52.000Z","msg":"就唱你老母李香籣"},{"pid":"d0ff8ab27ceef6f8e6340da8e7def0a0404459f8","tid":565243,"uid":57410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a66c3d562c369632f0a5bccbaa0bbc1e1ae8684","tid":565243,"uid":153418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T02:45:52.000Z","msg":"就唱你老母李